OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,FThe mother of Salisbury poisonings
OL,7,Fvictim Dawn Sturgess has said her
OL,8,Ffamily found comfort that she was the
OL,9,Fonly person to be killed by the
OL,10,FRussian nerve agent Novichok "when the
OL,11,Fpotential harm was much, much more".
OL,13,FCaroline Sturgess paid tribute to her
OL,14,Fdaughter at the Dawn Sturgess Inquiry
OL,15,Fon Tuesday, describing her as an
OL,16,F"intelligent...extremely selfless and
OL,17,Fvery kind person".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/15
