OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,FShe also read a short statement from
OL,7,FDawn's daughter, who cannot be named
OL,8,Ffor legal reasons, who said she never
OL,9,Fgot the chance to say goodbye to her
OL,10,Fmother due to her age.
OL,12,FCaroline told the inquiry that it is a
OL,13,F"solace" to her family that Dawn's
OL,14,Fdaughter was not killed in the
OL,15,Fincident.
OL,17,FDawn, 44, died after she was exposed
OL,18,Fto the chemical weapon, which was left
OL,19,Fin a discarded perfume bottle in
OL,20,FAmesbury, Wiltshire, in July 2018.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
