OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,FIt happened just a few months after
OL,7,Fthe attempted murder of former spy
OL,8,FSergei Skripal, his daughter Yulia and
OL,9,Fpolice officer Nick Bailey, who were
OL,10,Fpoisoned in nearby Salisbury.
OL,12,FMs Sturgess died after her boyfriend
OL,13,FCharlie Rowley unwittingly gave her a
OL,14,Fperfume bottle containing the nerve
OL,15,Fagent.
OL,17,FAn inquiry into her death, which
OL,18,Fstarted in Salisbury on Monday 14
OL,19,FOctober, heard there was "enough
OL,20,Fpoison to kill thousands of people" in
OL,21,Fthe bottle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/15
