OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,FGiving a short statement to the
OL,7,Finquiry from the witness box, Dawn's
OL,8,Fmother said: "Now, she would have been
OL,9,Fa grandmother but she will never have
OL,10,Fthe absolute joy of meeting her first
OL,11,Fgrandchild and doesn't get to watch
OL,12,Fher grow.
OL,14,F"She was an intelligent, funny,
OL,15,Fextremely selfless and very kind
OL,16,Fperson.
OL,18,F"She always cared deeply for her
OL,19,Ffamily and many friends that
OL,20,Fsurrounded her.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
