OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,F"She did not judge a single person and
OL,7,Fstrived to make others happy, even
OL,8,Fwhen she didn't feel like smiling
OL,9,Fherself."
OL,11,FIn a short statement made by Dawn's
OL,12,Fdaughter, read by Caroline, she said
OL,13,Fit was "heartbreaking" when she heard
OL,14,Fher mother had fallen ill.
OL,16,FShe said: "Me and my mum had a bond
OL,17,Fthat I will never forget.
OL,19,F"The day I heard she had fallen really
OL,20,Fill was heartbreaking to hear.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
