OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,F"In my mind I thought she would push
OL,7,Fthrough it because there was nothing
OL,8,Fmy mum couldn't handle.
OL,10,F"The day I heard everyone go to say
OL,11,Ftheir goodbyes when she was in
OL,12,Fintensive care was so upsetting.
OL,13,FShortly after she passed away.
OL,15,F"One thing I will never forget is due
OL,16,Fto my age I never saw her or got to
OL,17,Fsay goodbye."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
