OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,FHe apologised to the Sturgess family
OL,7,Fafter internal force documents
OL,8,Fsuggested Dawn was a "known drug user".
OL,10,FMr Mills said there were "reasons to
OL,11,Fsuspect that she may have become
OL,12,Funwell due to her association with
OL,13,Fdrugs", but added that there was "no
OL,14,Fpolice intelligence that she was a
OL,15,Fdrug user".
OL,17,FAddressing the last time she spoke to
OL,18,Fher daughter, Ms Sturgess continued:
OL,19,F"I last spoke to my daughter on the
OL,20,Fevening before the incident.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
