OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,F"We spoke at length about the
OL,7,Fexcitement she felt at the prospect of
OL,8,Ffinally leaving the hostel and living
OL,9,Findependently once more.
OL,11,F"The final part of our conversation
OL,12,Fthat night was discussing taking
OL,13,FDawn's daughter to her the following
OL,14,Fday to spend time together. She was to
OL,15,Fring me in the morning with a
OL,16,Fconfirmed time for me to drop her off.
OL,18,F"It was pure chance that Dawn had
OL,19,Fsprayed herself with the Novichok
OL,20,Fbefore her daughter arrived.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
