OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,F"Dawn's death was a tragedy to us all
OL,7,Fbut the fact that her daughter was not
OL,8,Fkilled as well is a solace that we
OL,9,Foften revisit."
OL,11,FMs Sturgess told the inquiry her
OL,12,Fdaughter's main priority was the
OL,13,Fwelfare of her children and she always
OL,14,Fgreeted her youngest daughter "on her
OL,15,Fknees so she could run into her arms".
OL,17,FShe said: "Dawn was raised in a
OL,18,Fnormal, loving, caring family in a
OL,19,Fvillage where most knew each other,
OL,20,Fand where the majority of our family
OL,21,Fstill live today.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
