OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,F"Her circumstances escalated to her
OL,7,Fliving in John Baker House for the
OL,8,Flast two years of her life.
OL,10,F"Dawn grasped this opportunity to
OL,11,Faddress her issues, she was excited
OL,12,Fthat it would be a new starting block
OL,13,Ffor a fresh chapter. She remained in
OL,14,Fconstant contact and was totally
OL,15,Fsupported by us all.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
