OL,3,CNovichok victim's mum says family took
OL,4,Ccomfort that nobody else died
OL,6,F"Dawn's main priority continued to be
OL,7,Fthe welfare of her children. Her
OL,8,Fyoungest ` still in primary school `
OL,9,Fwas always very excited to see her
OL,10,Fmum; I tried to take her in to see her
OL,11,Fas much as possible.
OL,13,F"They loved spending quality time
OL,14,Ftogether. Dawn always greeted her in
OL,15,Fthe same manner ` on her knees so she
OL,16,Fcould run into her arms."
OL,18,FConcluding her statement, Ms Sturgess
OL,19,Fsaid: "We understand that the perfume
OL,20,Fbottle contained enough Novichok to
OL,21,Fkill thousands of people.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
