OL,6,FAsked about the scale and complexity
OL,7,Fof the investigation, he told the
OL,8,Finquiry: "This was the first
OL,9,Fidentified use of a chemical weapon in
OL,10,Fthe UK, in this case, in this sense,
OL,11,Fused as a tool, we say, to conduct an
OL,12,Fassassination in this style.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/15
